== How to run application

* copy config/database.yml.tmp to config/database.yml and set up database
* copy config/settings.yml.tmp to config/settings.yml
* create app on Facebook and set them up in settings.yml (http://www.facebook.com/developers/apps.php)
* create new Maps API key for your development domain (e.g. localhost) and set it up in settings.yml (http://code.google.com/apis/maps/signup.html)

== How to run tests

* create separate app on Facebook for test environment, using http://127.0.0.1:3100/ as Site URL (or whatever your host name is, make sure to set correct port number)
* create new Maps API key with the same domain name
* run rake spec
